{"tid":914450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請問這裡有無負責人","createTime":"2018-11-24T09:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T10:05:45.000Z","uid":203734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"94d03b5239460186f4a098e9b78e8e23e9021a80","tid":914450,"uid":203734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:49:57.000Z","msg":"請問這裡有無負責人，為甚麼這裡有這麼多弱智級、兒童影片， <br />\n而沒人監管或移到兒童版， <br />\n本來我來貴壇，是嚴禁到兒童區， <br />\n以為就此沒問題。 <br />\n怎知道我們來到這裡，看到了那些弱智級影片， <br />\n變得心理開始有問題。 <br />\n請趕快妥善處理，否則，我向相關部門投訴。"},{"pid":"eaf4a6a98aa571ba8ababca764e13d88fa332c8a","tid":914450,"uid":203734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3358c54da8afd0ff503bb188a801d4e07b8d686d","tid":914450,"uid":203734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T10:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}